'''喬安娜·羅琳'''，[[名譽勳位|CH]]，[[官佐勳章|OBE]]，[[爱丁堡皇家学会会员|HonFRSE]]，[[爱丁堡皇家内科医师学会|FRCPE]]，[[皇家文學學會|FRSL]]<ref name="蔡明燁">{{Cite journal|author=蔡明燁|title=〈平凡與不平凡之間－J.K·羅琳〉|journal=《全國新書資訊月刊》|publisher=[[國家圖書館_(台灣)|國家圖書館]]|location=台北|volume=111|pages=60|url=http://isbn.ncl.edu.tw/NCL_ISBNNet/C00_index.php?Pfile=1524&KeepThis=true&...|format=pdf|language=zh-tw|accessdate=2013-08-30|date=2008年3月|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304193151/http://isbn.ncl.edu.tw/NCL_ISBNNet/C00_index.php?Pfile=1524&KeepThis=true&...|dead-url=no}}</ref>（{{lang-en|Joanne Rowling}}，{{bd|1965年|7月31日|catIdx=R羅}} ），笔名'''J·K·羅琳'''（{{lang-en|J. K. Rowling}}）及'''罗柏特·加尔布雷斯'''（{{lang-en|Robert Galbraith}}），[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[小说家|小说家]]、电影编剧及制片人，代表作為《[[哈利波特|哈利波特]]》系列作品<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://content.scholastic.com/browse/contributor.jsp?id=3578 |title=JK Rowling Biography |publisher=Scholastic.com |language=en |accessdate=2007-10-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071231114333/http://content.scholastic.com/browse/contributor.jsp?id=3578 |archivedate=2007-12-31 }}</ref><ref name=telegraph>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1531779/BBCs-secret-guide-to-avoid-tripping-over-your-tongue.html |title=BBC's secret guide to avoid tripping over your tongue |work=Daily Telegraph |language=en |date=2006-10-19 |accessdate=2011-11-17 |archive-date=2013-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130922041750/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1531779/BBCs-secret-guide-to-avoid-tripping-over-your-tongue.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她的《哈利波特》暢銷全球，熱賣超過4亿本，成為[[暢銷書列表|史上最暢銷的書籍之一]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Potter tops 400 million sales|author=Flood, Alison|work=theBookseller.com|url=http://www.thebookseller.com/news/potter-tops-400-million-sales.html|publisher=The Bookseller|language=en|date=2008-06-17|accessdate=2008-09-12|archive-date=2012-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118063000/http://www.thebookseller.com/news/potter-tops-400-million-sales.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Record for best-selling book series|url=http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/5000/best-selling-book-series-for-children|publisher=Guinness World Records|language=en|accessdate=2012-04-18|archive-date=2012-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023212942/http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/5000/best-selling-book-series-for-children|dead-url=no}}</ref>；其[[哈利波特系列电影|同名改編電影]]也成為[[最高電影票房收入列表|電影史上票房收入最高的電影]]之一<ref>{{cite web|title=Movie Franchises and Brands Index|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/?view=Franchise&sort=sumgross&order=DESC&p=.htm|publisher=Box Office Mojo|language=en|accessdate=2012-12-19|archive-date=2012-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120409170220/http://boxofficemojo.com/franchises/?view=Franchise&sort=sumgross&order=DESC&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該系列電影獲得羅琳的完整授權，她還親自擔任《[[哈利·波特与死亡圣器（上）|哈利·波特与死亡圣器（上）]]》和《[[哈利·波特与死亡圣器（下）|哈利·波特与死亡圣器（下）]]》的電影監製<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.firstshowing.net/2010/12/09/exclusive-interview-harry-potter-series-producer-david-heyman/|title=Exclusive Video Interview: 'Harry Potter' Producer David Heyman|publisher=firstshowing.net|language=en|year=2010|accessdate=2010-12-29|archive-date=2010-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101220175352/http://www.firstshowing.net/2010/12/09/exclusive-interview-harry-potter-series-producer-david-heyman/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Warner Bros. Pictures Worldwide Satellite Trailer Debut: Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows Part 1|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20100920005538/en/Warner-Bros.-Pictures-Worldwide-Satellite-Trailer-Debut%C2%A0Harry|publisher=Businesswire|year=2010|language=en|accessdate=2010-12-29|archive-date=2010-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101227092506/http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20100920005538/en/Warner-Bros.-Pictures-Worldwide-Satellite-Trailer-Debut%C2%A0Harry|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

J.K·羅琳生于[[英国|英国]][[格洛斯特郡|格洛斯特郡]][[葉特|葉特]]。1990年，當她在一班從[[曼徹斯特|曼徹斯特]]開往[[倫敦|倫敦]]的誤點列車上想到《哈利波特》小說靈感時，她是[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]的研究員兼雙語秘書<ref name=WizardBehindPotter>{{Cite book | last = Shapiro | first = Marc | title = ''J.K. Rowling: The Wizard Behind Harry Potter'' | publisher=St. Martin's Press | year = 2000 | location = New York | url = http://books.google.com/?id=7WZSQJ6aAwEC&dq=J.K.+Rowling |language=en| isbn = 0-312-32586-X}}</ref>。撰寫《[[哈利波特－神秘的魔法石|哈利波特－神秘的魔法石]]》期間，羅琳經歷貧窮、母親過世與首次離婚，終於在1997年出版《哈利波特》系列小說的第一本。其後續集逐年出版，最後一部《[[哈利波特－死神的聖物|哈利波特－死神的聖物]]》在2007年出版，宣告完結。羅琳的下一部作品與成名作完全不同，乃是面向成人讀者的[[悲喜劇|悲喜劇]]小說《[[臨時空缺|臨時空缺]]》，於2012年出版；2013年又以筆名「'''羅柏特·加爾布雷斯'''」（{{lang|en|Robert Galbraith}}）出版犯罪小說《[[布谷鸟的呼唤|杜鵑的呼喚]]》，羅琳表示此作將會發展成為系列小說。

J.K·羅琳的人生宛如《[[灰姑娘|灰姑娘]]》故事般，在短短5年內從接受政府濟助的貧窮單親媽媽成為富有的暢銷作家。她是英國有記錄以來最暢銷的作家，版稅所得約2,380萬英鎊<ref>{{cite web|title=JK Rowling: Casual Vacancy tops fiction charts|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/books/booknews/9584404/JK-Rowling-Casual-Vacancy-tops-fiction-charts.html|publisher=''The Telegraph''|language=en|accessdate=2012-10-04|archive-date=2012-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004003423/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/books/booknews/9584404/JK-Rowling-Casual-Vacancy-tops-fiction-charts.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年，《{{Link-en|星期日泰晤士報富豪榜|Sunday Times Rich List}}》估測羅琳的財產總值約5.6億英鎊，是英國第12位富有的女性<ref name="richlist">{{Cite web|url=http://business.timesonline.co.uk/tol/business/specials/rich_list/rich_list_search/?l=8 Women's Rich List&nbsp|title=Joanne Rowling|publisher=''[[星期日泰晤士報|The Sunday Times]]''|language=en|date=2008-04-27|accessdate=2008-05-20|archive-date=2009-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090502101348/http://business.timesonline.co.uk/tol/business/specials/rich_list/rich_list_search/?l=8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[富比士|富比士]]則將羅琳評為2007年最具影響力名人的第27位，《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》也以她「對{{Link-en|哈利波特迷|Harry Potter fandom}}在社會、道德與政治方面的影響」評為2007年[[時代年度風雲人物|時代年度風雲人物]]第二位<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/lists/2007/53/07celebrities_JK-Rowling_CRTT.html|title=No.48 J.K. Rowling|publisher=''[[富比士雜誌|Forbes Magazine]]''|language=en|date=2007-06-14|accessdate=2007-10-20|archive-date=2020-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705020745/https://www.forbes.com/lists/2007/53/07celebrities_JK-Rowling_CRTT.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.time.com/time/specials/2007/personoftheyear/article/0,28804,1690753_1695388_1695436,00.html|title=Person of the Year 2007 Runners-Up: J.K. Rowling|publisher=''Time Magazine''|language=en|date=2007-12-23|accessdate=2007-12-23|archive-date=2007-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071221164141/http://www.time.com/time/specials/2007/personoftheyear/article/0,28804,1690753_1695388_1695436,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年10月，《[[衛報|衛報]]》將羅琳評為全英國最具影響力的女性<ref name="htanna">{{cite news|title=Harry Potter creator JK Rowling named Most Influential Woman in the UK|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/2010/oct/11/harry-potter-jkrowling-influential-woman|work=Guardian|location=UK|accessdate=2010-10-11|first=Damien|last=Pearse|date=2010-10-11|language=en|archive-date=2013-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130702140056/http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/2010/oct/11/harry-potter-jkrowling-influential-woman|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她也投入[[慈善|慈善]]活動，支持[[喜劇救濟|喜劇救濟]]、{{Link-en|大不列顛多發性硬化症協會|Multiple Sclerosis Society of Great Britain}}、{{Link-en|薑餅 (慈善)|Gingerbread (charity)|薑餅}}、[[路摸思|路摸思]]等慈善團體。

== 名字 ==
雖然羅琳大多數時候都用她的筆名「J·K·羅琳」（{{lang|en|J. K. Rowling}}），在《哈利波特－神秘的魔法石》出版時卻直接使用本名「喬安娜·羅琳」（{{lang|en|Joanne Rowling}}）<ref name=bio>{{Cite web|url=http://www.accio-quote.org/articles/1998/autobiography.html|title="The Not Especially Fascinating Life So Far of J. K. Rowling"|author=J. K. Rowling|publisher=accio-quote.org|language=en|accessdate=2008-04-28|archive-date=2008-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080430125041/http://www.accio-quote.org/articles/1998/autobiography.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。出版社考慮此書的目標讀者群為小男孩，恐怕不會買女作家寫的書，遂建議她改用兩個字母縮寫作為筆名；但羅琳沒有[[中間名|中間名]]，於是選擇奶奶「凱薩琳」（{{lang|en|Kathleen}}）的「K」作為她筆名的第二個縮寫字母<ref>{{Cite episode |title=Jo Rowling Interview on Oprah |url=http://www.oprah.com/showinfo/Harry-Potter-Phenom-JK-Rowling |accessdate=2012-01-28 |language=en |series=The Oprah Winfrey Show |serieslink=The Oprah Winfrey Show |airdate=2010-10-01 |time=1:50 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111219121651/http://www.oprah.com/showinfo/Harry-Potter-Phenom-JK-Rowling |archivedate=2011-12-19 }}</ref>。她總稱自己為「喬」（{{lang|en|Jo}}），還說：「小時候沒人會叫我喬安娜，除非他們生氣了<ref>{{Cite web |author=Canadian Broadcasting Corporation |url=http://www.angelfire.com/mi3/cookarama/cbcint_1.html |title="J.K. Rowling: CBC Interview #1" |publisher=''The Hogwarts Express'' |language=en |date=2000-10-26 |accessdate=2006-03-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20011027070501/http://www.angelfire.com/mi3/cookarama/cbcint_1.html |archivedate=2001-10-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。」婚後，她有時會在處理個人私事時使用冠上夫姓的「喬安娜·莫瑞」（{{lang|en|Joanne Murray}}）<ref name=david>{{Cite web|url=http://books.guardian.co.uk/news/articles/0,,2143434,00.html|title=Judge rules against JK Rowling in privacy case|publisher=''Guardian Unlimited''|language=en|date=2007-08-07|accessdate=2007-08-21|archive-date=2008-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080608173816/http://books.guardian.co.uk/news/articles/0,,2143434,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=dt>{{Cite web|author=Greig, Geordie|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1507438/There-would-be-so-much-to-tell-her....html|title="There would be so much to tell her..."|publisher=''Daily Telegraph''|language=en|date=2006-01-10|accessdate=2010-08-08|archive-date=2007-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070311032026/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/main.jhtml?xml=%2Fnews%2F2006%2F01%2F10%2Fnrowl110.xml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{Link-en|利維森調查|Leveson Inquiry}}時，她則使用「喬安娜·凱薩琳·羅琳」（{{lang|en|Joanne Kathleen Rowling}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.levesoninquiry.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/Witness-Statement-of-JK-Rowling2.pdf|title=Witness statement of Joanne Kathleen Rowling|publisher=The Leveson Inquiry|date=2011-11|language=en|accessdate=25 November 2011|archive-url=http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20140122145147/http:/www.levesoninquiry.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/Witness-Statement-of-JK-Rowling2.pdf|archive-date=2014-01-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在2012年的訪談中，羅琳表示她並不介意人們誤解她筆名縮寫的意思<ref name=shelley>{{cite web|title=JK Rowling: 'The worst that can happen is that everyone says, That's shockingly bad'|author=Decca Aitkenhead|publisher=The Guardian|year=2012|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/2012/sep/22/jk-rowling-book-casual-vacancy|accessdate=2012-09-22|language=en|archive-date=2013-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130715042033/http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/2012/sep/22/jk-rowling-book-casual-vacancy|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

