 |last=VanHoose |title=Harry Potter’s Jason Isaacs Responds To JK Rowling Anti-Trans Controversy |url=https://screenrant.com/jk-rowling-controversy-harry-potter-jason-isaacs-comments/ |website=Screen Rant |accessdate=2022-01-24 |date=2022-01-20 |archive-date=2022-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220422144312/https://screenrant.com/jk-rowling-controversy-harry-potter-jason-isaacs-comments/ }}</ref>。鉴于与罗琳的争议，[[华纳兄弟公司|华纳兄弟公司]]也发表声明：「过去几周的事件坚定了我们作为一家公司面对困难的社会问题的决心。华纳兄弟公司在包容性方面的立场已经确立，并且对于我们公司和全球受众来说，培养多元化和包容性文化从未像现在这样重要。」<ref>{{Cite web|title=Warner Bros. Responds to J.K. Rowling Controversy – Media Play News|url=https://www.mediaplaynews.com/warner-bros-responds-to-j-k-rowling-controversy/|accessdate=2020-07-02|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925121029/https://www.mediaplaynews.com/warner-bros-responds-to-j-k-rowling-controversy/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Read Latest News, News Today, Breaking News, India News and Current News on Politics, Bollywood and Sports.|url=https://m.republicworld.com/|accessdate=2020-07-02|last=World|first=Republic|work=Republic World|language=en|archive-date=2020-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200416115613/https://m.republicworld.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

