J.K·羅琳曾獲[[聖安德魯斯大學|聖安德魯斯大學]]、[[愛丁堡大學|愛丁堡大學]]、[[愛丁堡納皮爾大學|愛丁堡納皮爾大學]]、[[艾希特大學|艾希特大學]]<ref>{{cite news|title=J K Rowling given honorary degree at her alma mater|author=Sally Pook|year=2001|work=Daily Telegraph|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1348603/J-K-Rowling-given-honorary-degree-at-her-alma-mater.html|location=London|date=2000-07-15|language=en|accessdate=2010-05-05|archive-date=2010-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100531003402/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1348603/J-K-Rowling-given-honorary-degree-at-her-alma-mater.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[亞伯丁大學|亞伯丁大學]]<ref>{{cite web|title=JK Rowling receives honorary degree|author=David Cribb|year=2006|work=digital spy|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/a34635/jk-rowling-receives-honorary-degree.html|language=en|accessdate=2008-06-06|archive-date=2008-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081210080930/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/a34635/jk-rowling-receives-honorary-degree.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title='Harry Potter' author JK Rowling receives Honorary Degree|work=University of Aberdeen|url=http://www.abdn.ac.uk/mediareleases/release.php?id=638|year=2006|language=en|accessdate=2008-06-06|archive-date=2008-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081212015310/http://www.abdn.ac.uk/mediareleases/release.php?id=638|dead-url=no}}</ref>及[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]頒發榮譽學位，其中羅琳曾在哈佛大學2008年畢業典禮上對畢業生演講<ref>{{cite web|title=J. K. Rowling To Speak at Commencement|author=Claire M. Guehenno and Laurence H. M. Holland|year=2008|work=The Harvard Crimson|url=http://www.thecrimson.com/article.aspx?ref=521567|language=en|accessdate=2008-06-06|archive-date=2008-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080615205621/http://www.thecrimson.com/article.aspx?ref=521567|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2009年，[[法國總統|法國總統]][[尼古拉·薩科齊|尼古拉·薩科齊]]向羅琳頒發[[法國榮譽軍團勳章|法國榮譽軍團勳章]]<ref name=legion/>。

